snippet.title: Look Your Loot. Gameplay preview.
snippet.description:
Html5-demo: http://dragosha.com/hamster/

Tap on neighbors card to make the turn. Explore, beat and reach a loot. 


p.s. Defeat the boss to add +1 to score multiplication.
